This library only supports Ruby 1.9.1 and is only tested to work on Mac OS X 10.6 Snow Leopard.

1. Initialise and update submodules

  - git submodule init
  - git submodule update

2. Compile the termios module

  - rake compile_termios

3. Run the test suite (please report back if you're seeing errors)

  - rake spec

3. Run an example!

  - ruby examples/your_choice.rb

